1
00:00:19,463 --> 00:00:26,554
Hakika umesikia kuhusu Herman Hollerith au kazi yake.

2
00:00:26,555 --> 00:00:31,710
Hakika, bila shaka! Hollerith alizaliwa

3
00:00:31,711 --> 00:00:34,829
Amerika mwaka wa 1860 kama mtoto wa wahamiaji wa Ujerumani,

4
00:00:34,830 --> 00:00:38,373
alimaliza masomo yake huko kama mhandisi wa madini

5
00:00:38,374 --> 00:00:43,038
na kisha akashughulika na takwimu katika umri mdogo.

6
00:00:43,039 --> 00:00:46,889
Chukua sensa ya 1880, kwa mfano:

7
00:00:46,890 --> 00:00:50,809
kazi zote za mwongozo zilizohusika katika kutathmini dodoso

8
00:00:50,810 --> 00:00:54,929
kwa usaidizi wa orodha za kujumlisha zilimfanya afikiri.

9
00:00:54,930 --> 00:01:01,462
Je, mashine hazikuweza kusaidia kupunguza muda wa tathmini wa karibu miaka kumi?

10
00:01:01,463 --> 00:01:05,116
Swali kuu lilikuwa ukusanyaji wa data

11
00:01:05,117 --> 00:01:08,405
, ambayo alikuwa akitafuta njia inayofaa

12
00:01:08,406 --> 00:01:12,418
ambayo ingefaa kwa usindikaji wa mitambo baadaye.

13
00:01:12,419 --> 00:01:16,005
Katika safari moja, aliona jinsi kondakta alitumia koleo kupiga

14
00:01:16,006 --> 00:01:18,275
sehemu mbalimbali za abiria

15
00:01:18,276 --> 00:01:21,424
kupitia matundu kwenye tikiti .

16
00:01:21,425 --> 00:01:24,767
Kwa mfano, jinsia au rangi ya ngozi.

17
00:01:24,768 --> 00:01:29,028
Hiyo hatimaye ilimpa wazo:

18
00:01:29,029 --> 00:01:32,818
Unaweza pia kutumia kanuni kwa takwimu

19
00:01:32,819 --> 00:01:38,425
na kuokoa sifa muhimu kwa msaada wa mashimo kwenye karatasi.

20
00:01:38,426 --> 00:01:41,200
Walakini, kunyakua na koleo ilikuwa ya kuchosha sana

21
00:01:41,201 --> 00:01:47,413
na pia sio sahihi kabisa. Kwa hiyo aliamua

22
00:01:47,414 --> 00:01:53,595
kujenga ngumi ya shimo. Punch hii inaitwa pantograph.

23
00:01:53,596 --> 00:01:58,736
Kadi ya punch imeingizwa kwenye pantografu

24
00:02:00,041 --> 00:02:04,023
na kwa kusonga mbele na nyuma kwa nafasi

25
00:02:04,024 --> 00:02:07,187
zinazowakilisha data inayotakiwa,

26
00:02:07,188 --> 00:02:11,174
kupiga ngumi hufanywa.

27
00:02:11,175 --> 00:02:16,651
Sasa ninatoboa mashimo machache bila mpangilio

28
00:02:17,798 --> 00:02:20,624
na unaona nafasi kumi na mbili za shimo hapa

29
00:02:20,625 --> 00:02:26,067
na nafasi 20 za mashimo kwa mlalo. SAWA!

30
00:02:27,239 --> 00:02:30,432
Hollerith alichagua umbizo la kadi ya punch

31
00:02:30,433 --> 00:02:33,707
yenye mistari kumi na mbili na safu wima 20.

32
00:02:33,708 --> 00:02:36,670
Onyesho lifuatalo

33
00:02:36,671 --> 00:02:39,722
linatumia jumla ya nafasi nne za matundu kwa magonjwa,

34
00:02:39,723 --> 00:02:47,353
yaani surua, kifua kikuu, diphtheria na mafua.

35
00:02:47,354 --> 00:02:54,772
Pia kuna nafasi mbili za shimo kwa sifa za kiume na za kike.

36
00:02:54,773 --> 00:02:58,887
Katika zifuatazo tunatumia kadi mbili "MM" kwa

37
00:02:58,895 --> 00:03:04,715
surua ya kiume na "DiW" kwa diphtheria ya kike.

38
00:03:07,020 --> 00:03:13,411
Sasa ramani inaonekana! Na moja zaidi! jamani, janga la surua!

39
00:03:13,412 --> 00:03:16,936
Hapa unaweza kuona counters kwa

40
00:03:16,937 --> 00:03:22,648
surua ya kiume, kifua kikuu, diphtheria na mafua.

41
00:03:22,653 --> 00:03:27,563
Na sawa kwa wanawake:

42
00:03:27,564 --> 00:03:33,837
surua ya kike, kifua kikuu, diphtheria na mafua.

43
00:03:35,338 --> 00:03:39,432
Msingi wa msomaji una mawasiliano ya sifa zote zinazopatikana

44
00:03:39,433 --> 00:03:46,424
kwa mfano surua, diphtheria, dume na jike.

45
00:03:46,425 --> 00:03:50,775
Mawasiliano yanaunganishwa kwa umeme kwenye vihesabu vinavyofaa na

46
00:03:50,776 --> 00:03:56,114
inaweza kuunganishwa kimantiki kwa usaidizi wa relays.

47
00:03:56,115 --> 00:03:59,857
Msomaji ana pini zilizojaa spring, ambazo

48
00:03:59,858 --> 00:04:03,384
pia zimeunganishwa na counters.

49
00:04:03,385 --> 00:04:06,401
Ikiwa unaingiza kadi ya punch na kisha

50
00:04:06,402 --> 00:04:12,497
huzuni lever ya kuhisi, ambapo kuna mashimo,

51
00:04:12,498 --> 00:04:19,298
mzunguko unafungwa na counter huongezeka kwa moja.

52
00:04:19,299 --> 00:04:24,372
Popote ambapo hakuna mashimo, hakuna mtiririko wa sasa

53
00:04:24,373 --> 00:04:29,896
na kwa hiyo kaunta hazijawashwa.

54
00:04:30,185 --> 00:04:34,311
Ndiyo basi bado tunapaswa kuchakata data za mtu mwingine

55
00:04:34,312 --> 00:04:37,928
ambaye ni diphtheria ya kike. Na ninapowasha

56
00:04:37,929 --> 00:04:41,826
kituo cha kusoma, unaona

57
00:04:41,827 --> 00:04:47,846
kwamba kaunta saba inaruka kwa jumlisha moja.

58
00:04:47,847 --> 00:04:51,558
Hollerith aligundua haraka kuwa

59
00:04:51,559 --> 00:04:56,330
kupanga kadi ni hatua muhimu.

60
00:04:56,331 --> 00:05:03,284
Sambamba na hisia ya kadi na harakati za vihesabio,

61
00:05:03,285 --> 00:05:12,998
piga moja hufungua kwenye kisanduku cha kuchagua kwa ajili ya kuhifadhi kadi ya surua ya kiume.

62
00:05:12,999 --> 00:05:20,134
Na tunaweza kuonyesha kitu kimoja na diphtheria ya kike,

63
00:05:20,135 --> 00:05:22,835
kwa hivyo somo la saba linafungua.

64
00:05:22,836 --> 00:05:26,465
Sasa kazi yote ikikamilika unaweza

65
00:05:26,466 --> 00:05:31,998
kuchukua kadi zilizopigwa kutoka kwa wapangaji

66
00:05:31,999 --> 00:05:37,404
na hapa ndipo kadi za kike zinatoka na hapa ndipo

67
00:05:37,405 --> 00:05:43,787
kadi za kiume zinatoka. Ikiwa unataka kuchambua ambapo

68
00:05:43,967 --> 00:05:51,209
kesi nyingi za surua hutokea, basi ninaweza tu kuchukua kadi za surua na kuzitathmini

69
00:05:51,210 --> 00:05:55,210
kwenye mashine nyingine, ambayo hatuna hapa sasa

70
00:05:55,215 --> 00:06:00,358
, lakini kulingana na mpango huu.

71
00:06:00,359 --> 00:06:04,410
Hiyo inamaanisha kuwa sasa una rundo la surua dume, kwa mfano

72
00:06:04,419 --> 00:06:09,364
na sifa zingine, kama vile umri, kwa mfano. Hasa!

73
00:06:09,365 --> 00:06:12,167
Hii inamaanisha kuwa tayari tumeshapanga kulingana na "surua ya kiume"

74
00:06:12,168 --> 00:06:14,934
na sasa unaweza kufanya moja zaidi na mashine ya pili.

75
00:06:14,935 --> 00:06:17,639
fanya takwimu za kina na ... haswa!

76
00:06:18,253 --> 00:06:26,064
Mwishowe, Herman Hollerith alifanikisha lengo lake! Katika sensa ya 1890,

77
00:06:26,065 --> 00:06:31,594
muda wa uchambuzi ulipunguzwa kutoka kumi hadi miaka miwili tu.

78
00:06:32,398 --> 00:06:35,935
Ngumi zake 500 zilitumika

79
00:06:35,936 --> 00:06:40,001
kuhamisha dodoso hadi kwenye kadi milioni 62 za ngumi

80
00:06:40,002 --> 00:06:44,209
, na kisha mifumo 90 ya kuhesabu

81
00:06:44,210 --> 00:06:46,203
hatimaye ikatathmini.

82
00:06:46,420 --> 00:06:50,241
Na mwisho kabisa, enzi mpya ya usindikaji wa data ya kielektroniki ilianza

83
00:06:50,242 --> 00:06:53,852
.

84
00:06:53,853 --> 00:06:57,316
Hatua ya kweli katika historia ya IT!

85
00:06:57,317 --> 00:07:00,318
Tungependa kumshukuru mhadhiri wetu Heinz Graichen

86
00:07:00,319 --> 00:07:04,532
ambaye, pamoja na wenzake,

87
00:07:04,533 --> 00:07:08,060
wameunda upya kinanda cha takwimu katika zaidi ya saa 2000 za kazi.

88
00:07:08,061 --> 00:07:13,077
Kwa njia, inasemekana kuwa kuna nakala mbili tu zilizobaki ulimwenguni

89
00:07:13,078 --> 00:07:18,261
! Asante kwa umakini wako na kwaheri!

